description: "The inset map on this map of India features part of mainland Southeast Asia: Pegu and the Tenasserim Provinces (Myanmar), Siam (Thailand), and the Malay Peninsula (Malaysia), with the Straits Settlements—Singapore, Malacca, Penang—highlighted in red."
title: "Plan of the Island Cocos / surveyed and drawn by Capt. James Colnett, 1793 ; engraved by T. Foot."
